{
  "stem": "214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was the first one in the family that got typhus, which is, you know, like fever, which really comes from the-- we were so [NON-ENGLISH]-- I mean, I think back, and I think this was one of the worst scourges.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were just eating you up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was the only one who had it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, it was still being-- I think I was quarantined.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were already in Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember another thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I came home, I was again, this one room, whatever we had in there was, also.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was-- I was so weak, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was-- people would come in and would say, you know, my face was-- would come in and say-- she looks like a Madonna, like Raphael's Madonna.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My face was so-- and really I couldn't even stand on my feet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember-- and this I don't want to tell, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because I always cry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My mother would go out every morning, maybe at 5 o'clock-- I don't know where she went-- and brought me [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] an orange.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I have no idea where she got it and how much she spent for it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Every time I think of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[CRYING] There are two places that I can't refrain from crying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, anyway, that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She would bring these oranges as if she think that this is going to make me well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- eating a piece of-- a small piece of black bread, if you were fortunate to buy it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was this Jewish bakery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was the name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], I think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would get-- if they had enough, they would also provide us with some bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
